briefdescription.para: Default constructor.

detaileddescription.para:
Default constructor.
atmosphereTableFile
Map of files containing information on the atmosphere. The order of both independent and dependent parameters needs to be specified in the independentVariablesNames and dependentVariablesNames vectors, respectively. Note that specific gas constant and specific heat ratio will be given the default constant values for Earth, unless they are included in the file map.
independentVariablesNames
List of independent parameters describing the atmosphere.
dependentVariablesNames
List of dependent parameters output by the atmosphere.
specificGasConstant
The constant specific gas constant of the atmosphere.
ratioOfSpecificHeats
The constant ratio of specific heats of the atmosphere.
boundaryHandling
List of methods for interpolation behavior when independent variable is out of range.
defaultExtrapolationValue
List of default values to be used for extrapolation, in case of use_default_value or use_default_value_with_warning as methods for boundaryHandling.

detaileddescription.para: Constructor with no specific gas constant nor ratio of specific heats, and with single boundary handling parameters.

Constructor with no specific gas constant nor ratio of specific heats. These two values will be given the default Earth value, or are specified inside the atmosphere table file (and thus, inside the dependent variables vector). Only one boundary handling parameter is specified, which is then repeated for dimension.
atmosphereTableFile
Map of files containing information on the atmosphere. The order of both independent and dependent parameters needs to be specified in the independentVariablesNames and dependentVariablesNames vectors, respectively. Note that specific gas constant and specific heat ratio will be given the default constant values for Earth, unless they are included in the file map.
independentVariablesNames
List of independent parameters describing the atmosphere.
dependentVariablesNames
List of dependent parameters output by the atmosphere.
boundaryHandling
Method for interpolation behavior when independent variable is out of range.
defaultExtrapolationValue
Default value to be used for extrapolation, in case of use_default_value or use_default_value_with_warning as methods for boundaryHandling.
